OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FThe family of a teenager who drowned
OL,8,Fin North Yorkshire have paid tribute
OL,9,Fto her and launched a fundraising
OL,10,Fappeal in her memory.
OL,12,FPalwasha Akbar, 13, died after being
OL,13,Fpulled from the River Wharfe near
OL,14,FBurnsall in the Skipton area after a
OL,15,Fshe was reported missing at around
OL,16,F6.30pm on Sunday 31 May.
OL,18,FHer family have now set up a GoFundme
OL,19,Ffundraising appeal in her memory where
OL,20,Fthey paid tribute to a "bright, kind,
OL,21,Fand caring 13-year-old girl".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FThey said: "Palwasha loved reading,
OL,8,Fspending time with her friends, and
OL,9,Fbringing happiness to those around
OL,10,Fher. She was a hardworking student
OL,11,Fwith a warm smile, a gentle nature,
OL,12,Fand a caring heart.
OL,14,F"She had a bright future ahead of her
OL,15,Fand touched the lives of so many
OL,16,Fpeople through her kindness and
OL,17,Fpositivity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,F"In memory of Palwasha, we are raising
OL,8,Ffunds to support charitable causes
OL,9,Fthat reflect the values she lived by `
OL,10,Fkindness, compassion, and helping
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"Through this fundraiser, we hope to
OL,14,Fcreate something positive and lasting
OL,15,Fin her name, ensuring that her memory
OL,16,Fcontinues to make a difference in the
OL,17,Flives of others."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FThey have thanked donors adding:
OL,8,F"Thank you for helping us remember a
OL,9,Fbeautiful young girl who was taken far
OL,10,Ftoo soon but will never be forgotten."
OL,12,FBronte Girls' Secondary Academy, in
OL,13,FBradford, paid have previously shared
OL,14,Ftributes to Palwasha.
OL,16,FActing principal Lyndsay Hall said:
OL,17,F"We are deeply saddened by the death
OL,18,Fof one of our much-loved students in a
OL,19,Fswimming accident. She was a valued
OL,20,Fand much-loved member of the school
OL,21,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
