PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FHer school form tutor Miss Wagstaff
OL,8,Fadded: "She will always be part of
OL,9,FBronte Girls Academy, woven into every
OL,10,Fhall, and carried in the hearts of
OL,11,Fthose who loved her most of all."
OL,13,FNorth Yorkshire police said on 31 May
OL,14,Fthat emergency services were called to
OL,15,Fthe River Wharfe when she had been
OL,16,Freported missing in the river.
OL,18,FA short time later she was rescued
OL,19,Ffrom the water and taken to hospital
OL,20,Fby air ambulance where she died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
