PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FA police spokesperson said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with her family.
OL,10,F"Our thanks go to the members of the
OL,11,Fpublic who helped at the scene."
OL,13,FPalwasha is one of six young people
OL,14,Fwho lost their lives in open water
OL,15,Facross the Calendar region during the
OL,16,Fhot half-term weather.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
