OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781032284
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'kind, and
OL,4,Ccaring' 13-year-old who drowned last
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FDeclan Sawyer, 15, died after an
OL,8,Fincident at Swanholme Lakes in
OL,9,FLincolnshire. Another 13-year-old Reco
OL,10,FPuttock, died at Leadbeater Dam in
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire. Muhammad Secka, 17
OL,12,Fdied after getting in trouble at
OL,13,FRother Valley Country Park in South
OL,14,FYorkshire. Mackenzie Swift, 11, died
OL,15,Fin the river Don near Mexborough and
OL,16,Fan unnamed man aged 19 who died after
OL,17,Fbeing pulled from Balderton Lake near
OL,18,FNewark.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
